he kitchen to make a healthy green juice in my slow juicer. I always try to use organic ingredients, but I still make sure to clean them well.</span></p></div></div><div class="sc-pbYdQ jklmHY pf-c pf-c-xs--12 pf-c-sm--12 pf-c-md--12 pf-c-lg--12"><div class="sc-pkUyL fTyjzF pf-9eaf48c0" data-pf-type="Column"><img sizes="(min-width: 992px) 1200px, (min-width: 768px) and (max-width: 991px) 800px, 400px" data-srcset="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0277/5859/2073/t/3/assets/pf-b0707a9f--3F577EC80B5B49198A4CB9CE2A0F2F79-1-Edited.jpg?v=1598800170 1200w, https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0277/5859/2073/t/3/assets/pf-b0707a9f--3F577EC80B5B49198A4CB9CE2A0F2F79-1-Edited_800x722.jpg?v=1598800170&resized 800w, https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0277/5859/2073/t/3/assets/pf-b0707a9f--3F577EC80B5B49198A4CB9CE2A0F2F79-1-Edited_400x361.jpg?v=1598800170&resized 400w" srcset="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEKAAEALAAAAAABAAEAAAICTAEAOw==" class="sc-qZtVr dLIPjF pf-af48c0f4 pf-img-lazy" data-pf-type="Image2"></div></div><div class="sc-pbYdQ jklmHY pf-c pf-c-xs--12 pf-c-sm--12 pf-c-md--12 pf-c-lg--12"><div class="sc-pkUyL fTyjzF pf-6b589256" data-pf-type="Column"><h3 data-pf-type="Heading" class="sc-oTLFK lcHmGL pf-61e847ed"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-ptSuy fnmilh pf-c0f4d3a0">Healthy Juice Recipe: Green Wellness<br></span></h3><p data-pf-type="Paragraph2" class="sc-pkvvt cbrLgP pf-f76b5892"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-ptSuy fnmilh pf-d3a00059">1 stalk of celery<br>1 lemon<br>1 handfull spinach<br>1 handfull kale<br>5 cm ginger<br><br>Run the ingredients through a slow juicer. If you do not have a slow juicer, use a normal blender with 100 ml of water, and strain out the water after blending. I then bring the juice over to my yoga mat.<br></span></p></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div data-container="true" class="sc-pZopv bjKdkd pf-981f275c" data-pf-type="Section"><div class="sc-pQQXS iWCqut" style="max-width: 1170px;"><